{
  "stem": "3382.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said, you won't be sorry, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I started to work there, in the military barracks, on Snipiskes there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I worked there all the time, always coming up with a column.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Now-- [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] and then the rumors started to circulate that we will be put in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Let me tell one thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In-between, in Vilna, were terrible things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They used to catch Jews from streets, take them to the prison-- Lukiszki-- from there to the suburban place, Ponary, or, in Jewish, [NON-ENGLISH], and shoot them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they took away one of my good friends, Jacob Gordon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He had a timber business, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he disappeared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then another somebody disappeared-- and just disappeared, it seemed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The people were-- and started that-- supposedly, they went somewhere to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But then, once I met the-- my Wanda Rewenska, who said, they didn't disappear.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were all shot in Ponary, all shot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There is, she said, a big ditch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And every day there is constant, incessant shooting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You should be careful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, now--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] [PAUSES FOR 12 SECONDS] It was-- we worked there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I came over as a [NON-ENGLISH]-- very interesting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you work for Wehrmacht, it means for the army-- and by and large, at that time they were not so dehumanized and so on-- victorious.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were very pleasant people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then came the Einsatzgruppen, the SS men.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the sergeant-- I work as an interpreter there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I told them, now be careful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The [GERMAN] has come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[GERMAN]-- this is how he would talk about them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then they disappeared, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They moved out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was very hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were beatings.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we had to bribe everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
